invalid type: string "Many of the European immigrants arrived in Uruguay in the late 1800s and have heavily\ninfluenced the architecture and culture of Montevideo and other major cities. For this\nreason, Montevideo and life within the city are reminiscent of parts of Europe. For\nexample Barcelona, Thessaloniki or Tel-Aviv are said to be similar to Montevideo in\ndifferent aspects /ref>", expecte